Output docs/images/cli-diff.gif

Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 980
Set Height 480
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Hide
Type "export HOME=/tmp/portal-demo-home" Enter
